  calc
    x * (x + 3) * (x + 3) = Nat.lcm a 40 * Nat.gcd a 40 := by 
      rw [h₂, h₁]
      <;> ring
    _ = (Nat.lcm a 40 * Nat.gcd a 40) := by ring
    _ = a * 40 := by 
      rw [Nat.gcd_mul_lcm a 40]
    _ = 40 * a := by 
      ring
```

So we have $x \cdot (x + 3)^2 = 40a$. This is a key equation.

