- For $x = 2$: $2 \cdot (2 + 3)^2 = 2 \cdot 25 = 50 \leq 320$
- For $x = 3$: $3 \cdot (3 + 3)^2 = 3 \cdot 36 = 108 \leq 320$
- For $x = 4$: $4 \cdot (4 + 3)^2 = 4 \cdot 49 = 196 \leq 320$
- For $x = 5$: $5 \cdot (5 + 3)^2 = 5 \cdot 64 = 320 \leq 320$
- For $x = 6$: $6 \cdot (6 + 3)^2 = 6 \cdot 81 = 486 > 320$

So $x \leq 5$.

