  - Divisible by 6: 6, 18
  - Check $\gcd(6, 40) = 2 \neq 6$ (invalid)
  - Check $\gcd(18, 40) = 2 \neq 6$ (invalid)
  - So x=3 invalid
- $x = 4$: $\gcd(a, 40) = 7$, $\text{lcm}(a, 40) = 28$
